# GetAnyNumberOnline — Cursor Project Rules

**Cursor agent rules (canonical for the AI):** This project uses **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** — YAML frontmatter + Markdown in the format Cursor loads for project rules. Files `01–03` are **always applied**; `04–05` apply when editing matching paths (`supabase/functions/**`, `src/lib/api.ts`). Keep this `rules.md` as human-readable documentation; when changing project conventions, update the **`.mdc`** sources first so the agent stays in sync.

