## Database Schema — Know this exactly

### profiles

- id UUID PK (references auth.users)
- email TEXT
- balance NUMERIC(12,4) — never goes below 0
- currency TEXT default 'USD'
- is_banned BOOLEAN
- created_at, updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ

### orders

- id UUID PK
- user_id UUID FK → profiles
- smspool_order_id TEXT
- smspool_number TEXT
- country TEXT (SMSPool ID)
- country_name TEXT (human readable)
- service TEXT (SMSPool ID)
- service_name TEXT (human readable)
- cost NUMERIC(10,4)
- status: pending | active | cancelled | expired | refunded
- expires_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- created_at, updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ

### messages

- id UUID PK
- order_id UUID FK → orders
- user_id UUID FK → profiles
- sender TEXT
- full_sms TEXT
- code TEXT (extracted OTP)
- received_at TIMESTAMPTZ

### transactions

- id UUID PK
- user_id UUID FK → profiles
- order_id UUID FK → orders (nullable)
- type: topup | deduction | refund
- amount NUMERIC(10,4)
- balance_before NUMERIC(12,4)
- balance_after NUMERIC(12,4)
- provider TEXT
- provider_ref TEXT
- provider_meta JSONB
- status: pending | completed | failed
- note TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ

### rentals

- id UUID PK
- user_id UUID FK → profiles
- smspool_rental_code TEXT
- smspool_rental_id TEXT
- phone_number TEXT
- country TEXT
- country_name TEXT
- service TEXT
- service_name TEXT
- days INT
- cost NUMERIC(10,4)
- status TEXT: active | expired | cancelled
- auto_extend BOOLEAN
- expires_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- created_at, updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ

### rental_messages

- id UUID PK
- rental_id UUID FK → rentals
- user_id UUID FK → profiles
- sender TEXT
- full_sms TEXT
- code TEXT
- received_at TIMESTAMPTZ

