## Supabase RPC Functions — Use these for ALL balance operations

- `deduct_balance_and_create_order(p_user_id, p_cost, p_country, p_country_name, p_service, p_service_name, p_pool)` → UUID
- `deduct_balance_and_create_rental(p_user_id, p_cost, p_country, p_country_name, p_service, p_service_name, p_days, p_rental_id)` → UUID
- `credit_balance(p_user_id, p_amount, p_type, p_order_id, p_provider, p_provider_ref, p_note)` → void
- `deliver_sms_message(p_order_id, p_user_id, p_sender, p_full_sms, p_code)` → void
- `update_order_smspool_details(p_order_id, p_smspool_order_id, p_smspool_number)` → void

NEVER update profiles.balance directly. Always use an RPC.

