## SMSPool API Rules

- ALL SMSPool calls go through Supabase Edge Functions — NEVER from Next.js API routes, NEVER from the browser
- SMSPool uses FormData POST — never JSON
- Public endpoints (catalog, pricing, country list, service list) still go through Edge Functions because the API key must stay server-side
- Never create a Next.js API route that calls SMSPool

