## Deployment Rules

After ANY Edge Function change:

1. `supabase functions deploy {function-name}`
2. Go to Supabase Dashboard → Edge Functions → {function} → Settings → toggle OFF "Verify JWT with legacy secret"

After ANY frontend change:

1. `vercel --prod`

After adding ANY new environment variable:

1. Add to .env.local
2. Add to Vercel dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables
3. Redeploy Vercel

