## What NOT to build

- Never create Next.js API routes that proxy SMSPool — use Edge Functions
- Never call SMSPool from the browser
- Never update profiles.balance directly from frontend — always use RPC
- Never store sensitive keys in .env.local that should be in Supabase secrets
- Never add calling/voice features — SMS only for now
- Never add social auth — email/password only for now
- Never install shadcn, radix, chakra, or any component library
